sub_title: New Business Development Officer at FUJIFILM Europe B.V
summary: Open Innovation facilitator, hi-tech enthusiast, green energy evangelist and startup savvy. Born in Athens, I have an MEng in Mechanical Engineering from the University of Patras and an MSc in Entrepreneurship & Innovation Management from the Royal Institute of Technology (KTH) in Stockholm. Currently I am exploring innovative business ideas and technologies in the fields of life sciences, energy and cleantech to secure future growth for Fujifilm.
